    public interface Tx_Extbase_DomainObject_DomainObjectInterface

    A Domain Object Interface. All domain objects which should be persisted need to implement the below interface.
    Usually you will need to subclass Tx_Extbase_DomainObject_AbstractEntity and Tx_Extbase_DomainObject_AbstractValueObject instead.
